\v 4 uNkulunkulu efakaza kanye la\add bo\add* ngezibonakaliso\x + 7.14. Mark. 16.20.\x*\x + Seb. 5.12.\x* lezimangaliso\x + Seb. 5.12.\x*, lemisebenzi yamandla eyizinhlobonhlobo\x + 6.4,5. 1 Thes. 1.5.\x*\x + Seb. 2.22. 1 Kor. 2.4.\x*, lokwabelwa kukaMoya oNgcwele\x + 6.4,5. 1 Thes. 1.5.\x*, njengokwentando yakhe\x + Efe. 1.5.\x*.
