\v 7 Wamenza waba phansi kancinyane kulezingilosi; wamethwesa umqhele wenkazimulo lodumo; wammisa phezu kwemisebenzi yezandla zakho;
\v 8 izinto zonke\x + Efe. 1.22. Fil. 3.21. Mat. 28.18.\x* wazehlisela ngaphansi kwenyawo zakhe. Ngoba ekwehliseni izinto zonke ngaphansi kwakhe, katshiyanga lutho olungehliselwanga kuye. Kodwa khathesi kasikaziboni izinto zonke zehliselwe kuye\x + 1 Kor. 15.25.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa siyambona uJesu, owenziwa waba phansi kancinyane kulezingilosi\x + 2.7. 1 Pet. 1.21.\x*\x + Joha. 10.17. Seb. 2.33. Fil. 2.7-9.\x*, ngenxa yenhlupheko yokufa\x + Joha. 10.17. Seb. 2.33. Fil. 2.7-9.\x*\x + 2.10. 5.12. 6.7.\x*, etheswe umqhele wobukhosi lodumo\x + 4.15,16; 5.2. 3.1.\x*, ukuze ngomusa kaNkulunkulu azwele\x + Mat. 16.28.\x* wonke ukufa\x + Joha. 12.32. Roma 5.18; 8.32. 2 Kor. 5.15. 1 Tim. 2.6. 1 Joha. 2.2.\x*.
